      "message": "[🟡 Suggestion] Line 110: `setupDeviceAuthObserver()` subscribes every time `start()` is called, and the new buffering logic means duplicate subscriptions can now append and replay the same auth result multiple times. If this view model can be restarted or the view lifecycle calls `start()` more than once, auth state transitions may be duplicated or rejected as invalid. Make observer installation idempotent, or reset/dispose the previous subscription before installing a new one.",
