      "message": "[🟡 Suggestion] Line 245: The Task now runs on the MainActor, but `try await accountsService.createTemporaryAccount()` is not handled. If account creation throws, the task fails silently and the UI remains in `.initial` with an installed auth observer and no user-visible error. Please catch the error and transition to the existing failure/error state used by this flow. For example:\n```suggestion\nTask { @MainActor in\n    do {\n        tempAccount \u003d try await accountsService.createTemporaryAccount()\n        let matched \u003d pendingAuthResults.filter { $0.accountId \u003d\u003d tempAccount }\n        pendingAuthResults.removeAll()\n        for result in matched {\n            updateDeviceAuthState(result: result)\n        }\n    } catch {\n        pendingAuthResults.removeAll()\n        uiState \u003d .error\n    }\n}\n```",
